                <h1>Trial for expelled McLeod delayed for second time</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/8ff743a4-382c-4a7d-a8ec-167ea2cd4656.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

